"update": 1,
"values": ["[wave amp=2 ][font=res://assets/font/yoster.ttf] [center] I know, you are pressing buttons, but nothing is happening. [/center] [/font] [/wave]", "[wave amp=2 ][font=res://assets/font/yoster.ttf] [center][/center] [/font] [/wave]", "[wave amp=2 ][font=res://assets/font/yoster.ttf] [center]I’ll ask you a little bit of 
patience...[/center] [/font] [/wave]
", "[wave amp=2 ][font=res://assets/font/yoster.ttf] [center][/center] [/font] [/wave]
", "[wave amp=2 ][font=res://assets/font/yoster.ttf][center]This little shadow wants to take his own path from my darkness; and I’d like that too.[/center] [/font] [/wave]
", "[wave amp=2 ][font=res://assets/font/yoster.ttf][center][/center] [/font] [/wave]", "[wave amp=2 ][font=res://assets/font/yoster.ttf][center]I have a favor to ask.[/center] [/font] [/wave]", "[wave amp=2 ][font=res://assets/font/yoster.ttf][center][/center] [/font] [/wave]", "[wave amp=2 ][font=res://assets/font/yoster.ttf][center]Take him with you, I’ll provide you with the tools to guide him, and you’ll build and take this road
 together.[/center] [/font] [/wave]", "[wave amp=2 ][font=res://assets/font/yoster.ttf][center][/center] [/font] [/wave]", "[wave amp=2 ][font=res://assets/font/yoster.ttf][center]If you agree, I’ll let you press “Select” or “E” to begin walking along this little shadow.[/center] [/font] [/wave]", "[wave amp=2 ][font=res://assets/font/yoster.ttf][center][/center] [/font] [/wave]"]
}
